	   <tr><td colspan=2>AP will outdamage the DMF due to the 2 handed damage bonus. On the surface it looks like the DMF is the superior weapon, but 1 handers have a low static damage bonus. So the AP will actually put out significantly more damage then the DMF even though it has a better ratio.<br>I'd bet AP puts out 20% more damage than the DMF. <br><br>This weapon will perform alot better than you think again due to the damage bonus. On a 1 hander it's always the same, so the faster weapons actually parse out ahead of the slower ones with better ratios.<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
